metadata.name: Anger and darkness
metadata.description:
The crow with its gray wings reminds us of the darkness of the night, which is a sign of death and anger
  which carries a symbol on its wings.
But in anger and tolerating anger, it brings us transformation
So be patient in the time of anger so that life is full of love and transformation
